      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modeled as isotropic linear-elastic up to yield, then bilinear isotropic hardening. Literature supports this formulation for quasi-static monotonic loading. UHMWPE vertebral body blocks modeled as elastic-perfectly-plastic consistent with ASTM F1717 material specification. Model form uncertainty quantified via literature bounds on material constants."
